  <brief_title>Risk Factors for Cytomegalovirus Disease in Solid Organ Transplantation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Predictors of Late-onset CMV Disease in Solid Organ Transplant Recipients: A Strategy to Improve the Benefits and Reduce the Risks of Anti-CMV Prophylaxis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
